  "body": "### Description\nThis issue was seen our our nodes. After the waves of voluntary exits during Capella, our Voluntary Exit operation pool never clear out completely and were sitting there with 47 operations in the pool for a long time.\n\n![image.png](https://images.zenhubusercontent.com/5e7019978ec11b7684ec1dd8/e8c146bb-12e6-4bb2-b89b-5188ce2ceace)\n\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\nNot sure yet.\n\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\n- Operations must be removed from the pool once they are seen in a block.\n\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\n- Some operations were not removed from the pool.\n\n**Frequency:** [How regularly does it occur?]\nUncertain.\n\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\n* 23.3.1",
